2008-02-26 08:41 (CET), Tobias Eriksson <tobias@cention.net>

 * The variables slant and weight are directly type cast instead of the way
   it was before in Cairo.Context.selectFontFace().
 * The constructors for the class Cairo.ImageSurface now takes format as an
   argument.
 * Removed the check against LONG_MAX in the constructor for Cairo.ImageSurface
   because it was really ugly. But some check should be made.

